thread.title: Hayden Fennell

author: Hayden Fennell
title: Hayden Fennell
text: Happy with all the processes , very easy transaction at the airport , only fault was the insurance option , as we took the one online it's a third party insurance , hence would have to pay rental car on the day then claim and wait up to two months to be reimbursed, wish you could allow the rental company's personals insurance option on your website
